article.description: — Jaheam Cornwall had 20 points as Gardner-Webb defeated Radford 69-57 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Cornwall scores 20 to carry Gardner-Webb past Radford 69-57
article.linkText: Cornwall scores 20 to carry Gardner-Webb past Radford 69-57
article.story: RADFORD, Va. -- — Jaheam Cornwall had 20 points as Gardner-Webb defeated Radford 69-57 on Wednesday night. Jacob Falko had 18 points for Gardner-Webb (9-14, 8-10 Big South Conference), which ended its five-game road losing streak. Jamaine Mann added 10 points, six rebounds and four blocks. Fah'Mir Ali had 11 points for the Highlanders (13-10, 12-5). Xavier Lipscomb and Lewis Djonkam each had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
